              <%= Settings.site.short_name %> now offers small businesses the option to make their premium payments online through secure electronic check payment. Use the link below and follow the instructions in <a href="https://dchealthlink.com/sites/default/files/v2/forms/Employers-Paying-Your-Premiums-Online.pdf"> Employers Paying Your Premiums Online guide</a> to make your premium payment online here: <a href="https://www.e-BillExpress.com/ebpp/DCHealthPay"> https://www.e-BillExpress.com/ebpp/DCHealthPay.</a>.
              <br> <br>

              <strong>To make a secure electronic check payment by phone</strong>
              <br>Call <%= notice.hbe.phone %> (LINK)
              <br>Select your language (1 for English, 2 for Spanish, additional language options available)
